<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbc369dbe-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s2996l"><num value="2996l">§ 2996l.</num><heading> Reservation of right to repeal, alter, or amend</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The right to repeal, alter, or amend this subchapter at any time is expressly reserved.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idbc369dbf-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/88/452/tX/s1013">Pub. L. 88–452, title X, § 1013</ref>, as added <ref href="/us/pl/93/355/s2">Pub. L. 93–355, § 2</ref>, <date date="1974-07-25">July 25, 1974</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/88/388">88 Stat. 388</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
